channel.title: Comments on: Sufjan Stevens and his Orchestra ride the BQE

item.title: By: bigcitysheep

item.description: So, does this mean that Sufjan's next state is going to be New York? At the pace he's on, he's going to have to live to 150 to get to all the states.
